---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---
<Layout metadata={{ title: 'About Yinkor' }}>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">About Yinkor Limited</h1>
    <div class="prose max-w-3xl mt-6">
      <p>Yinkor is a global industrial automation product supplier, providing flow, pressure, temperature, level, analysis and control instruments from world-leading brands.</p>
      <p>We are a high-volume buyer of Emerson, E+H, Yokogawa, Siemens, Honeywell, ABB, Cameron, and Chuanyi, enabling us to offer project discounts and competitive pricing.</p>
      <p>Unlike ordinary traders, we understand technology and provide professional sizing and selection support.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>